# CODEOWNERS — controls who must review changes to specific paths.
# Last matching rule wins. Adjust usernames/teams to match your org.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: all changes require review from a lead
*                               @your-org/leads

# Infrastructure & CI changes require a second set of eyes
.github/                        @your-org/leads @your-org/devops
infrastructure/                 @your-org/leads @your-org/devops

# AI/prompt changes require AI lead sign-off
server/src/prompts/             @your-org/ai-lead
server/src/agents/              @your-org/ai-lead
server/src/evals/               @your-org/ai-lead

# Security-sensitive middleware
server/src/middleware/auth.ts   @your-org/leads
server/src/middleware/rbac.ts   @your-org/leads
